      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t我只说在美国对于以下工作不能有工作服外显露纹身的规定：<br/>\nMilitary <br/>\nAirlines <br/>\nMedical Professionals <br/>\nActors <br/>\nTeachers/Educators<br/>\nLaw Enforcement <br/>\nCorporate <br/>\nLegal <br/>\nBanking and Finance <br/>\nHospitality <br/>\nSocial Workers<br/>\nModels<br/>\nUPS<br/>\n几乎所有decent的工作都有针对纹身显露的规定。<br/>\n建议是不管在国内外，都不要在衣服能遮挡的部位之外纹身。<br/>\n来源：<br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly90YXR0MmF3YXkuY29tL2Jsb2cvNS1qb2JzLXRoYXQtZG9udC1hbGxvdy10YXR0b29zLw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://tatt2away.com/blog/5-jobs-that-dont-allow-tattoos/\">https://tatt2away.com/blog/5-jobs-that-dont-allow-tattoos/</a> </div>",
